{"title":"apache实现二级域名访问不同项目目录","date":"2018-05-09T01:39:00.000Z","link":"post/62","tags":["p","servername","www","别名","参数","命令","域名","文件","服务器","目录"],"categories":["Liunx"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:31:53.827Z","content":"<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"1、注册二级域名\">1、注册二级域名<a href=\"post/62#1、注册二级域名\"></a></h1><p><a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/29716.html?spm=5176.11065259.1996646101.searchclickresult.5a6e32d4vSVPsQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/29716.html?spm=5176.11065259.1996646101.searchclickresult.5a6e32d4vSVPsQ</a></p>\n<p>域名——解析——添加解析<br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/1762603534.png\" alt><br>其实你申请的域名就是一个一级域名了。这样填写就是一个二级域名</p>\n<h1 id=\"2、apache设置虚拟主机VirtualHost配置文件\">2、apache设置虚拟主机VirtualHost配置文件<a href=\"post/62#2、apache设置虚拟主机VirtualHost配置文件\"></a></h1><p>只需在http.conf文件最后添加<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ServerName map.swj233.top //你的域名</span><br><span class=\"line\">DocumentRoot /var/www/maps //项目地址</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> 项目地址一定要写全！不能只写<br><code>/www/maps</code> 。这样会访问不到的。<br>方法：进入项目目录。<strong>pwd命令</strong>获得目录即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"虚拟主机配置参数：\">虚拟主机配置参数：<a href=\"post/62#虚拟主机配置参数：\"></a></h2><p>ServerAdmin  管理员邮箱</p>\n<p>DocumentRoot  指向服务器子目录路径</p>\n<p>ServerName  域名别名，可以设置多个别名同时指向当前目录，也可不填别名</p>\n<p>ErrorLog   错误日志保存位置</p>\n<p>CustomLog  访问日志保存位置</p>\n<p>ServerAlias 域名别名<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">例 :</span><br><span class=\"line\">别名，访问www.baidu.com www.baidu.com.cn都会解析到这个目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;VirtualHost www.baidu.com:80&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">DocumentRoot /var/www/html/sale</span><br><span class=\"line\">ServerName baidu.cn</span><br><span class=\"line\">ServerAlias www.baidu.cn www.baidu.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"百度语音demo","link":"post/64"},"next":{"title":"win7下用xampp部署php项目","link":"post/58"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/62/","toc":[{"title":"1、注册二级域名","id":"1、注册二级域名","index":"1"},{"title":"2、apache设置虚拟主机VirtualHost配置文件","id":"2、apache设置虚拟主机VirtualHost配置文件","index":"2","children":[{"title":"虚拟主机配置参数：","id":"虚拟主机配置参数：","index":"2.1"}]}]}